title: MPSC Notification 2025 - Apply Offline for Member Posts
description: The Maharashtra Public Service Commission (MPSC) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Member Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed Any Degree can apply for the MPSC Notification 2025. The interested applicants can apply in offline mode.
